== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
起初於2011年10月，[[索尼影業|索尼影業]]正與[[育碧影業|育碧影業]]作《刺客教條》真人電影的最後談判<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2011/digital/news/sony-targets-assassin-s-creed-for-bigscreen-1118044759/|title=Sony breeds 'Creed'|work=Variety|first=Marc|last=Graser|date=2011-10-20|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201184654/https://variety.com/2011/digital/news/sony-targets-assassin-s-creed-for-bigscreen-1118044759/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並公布將發行[[3D|3D]]版<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2011/film/news/gallic-vidgamer-ubisoft-lines-up-3-features-1118037076/|title=Gallic vidgamer Ubisoft lines up 3 features|last1=Keslassy|first1=Elsa|last2=Hopewell|first2=John|work=Variety|date=2011-05-15|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618014326/https://variety.com/2011/film/news/gallic-vidgamer-ubisoft-lines-up-3-features-1118037076/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，[[索尼影業|索尼影業]]和育碧之間的談判被擱置，育碧高層希望保留掌控電影的自主開發權。而[[索尼影業|索尼]]仍可負責發行電影，但直到宣布編劇和導演，育碧表示不會恢復談判<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2012/digital/news/fassbender-game-for-assassin-s-creed-1118056333/|title=Fassbender game for ‘Assassin’s Creed’|last1=Graser|first1=Marc|last2=Keslassy|first2=Elsa|work=Variety|date=2012-07-09|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112041341/https://variety.com/2012/digital/news/fassbender-game-for-assassin-s-creed-1118056333/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，育碧透露電影將和[[Regency_Enterprises|New Regency]][[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]共同製作並由他們發行。New Regency將資助電影部分製作，這為使育碧不必承擔太大的金融風險，但仍可參與創作。[[朱利安·巴羅|朱利安·巴羅]]內特還透露育碧希望隨著新遊戲推出而使電影發展成一個系列<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2012/digital/news/new-regency-fox-partner-on-ubisoft-s-assassin-s-creed-1118061053/|title=New Regency, Fox partner on Ubisoft’s ‘Assassin’s Creed’|last=Graser|first=Marc|work=Variety|date=2012-10-22|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704231700/http://variety.com/2012/digital/news/new-regency-fox-partner-on-ubisoft-s-assassin-s-creed-1118061053/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年1月，[[麥可·萊斯利|麥可·萊斯利]]被聘為編劇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/assassins-creed-movie-michael-lesslie-412273|title=New Regency and Ubisoft Tap Brit Writer for 'Assassin's Creed' Film (Exclusive)|last=Siegel|first=Tatiana|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-01-14|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2014-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141123133212/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/assassins-creed-movie-michael-lesslie-412273|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年5月，宣布[[電影|電影]]將在2015年5月22日上映<ref name="ACrelease">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/05/18/assassins-creed-movie-slated-for-2015-release|title=Assassin's Creed Movie Slated for 2015 Release|last=Vejvoda|first=Jim|publisher=IGN|date=2013-05-17|accessdate=2013-05-18|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224131932/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/05/18/assassins-creed-movie-slated-for-2015-release|dead-url=no}}</ref>，後改為2015年6月19日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/21/fox-shuffles-x-men-apes-and-assassins-creede|title=Fox Shuffles X-Men, Apes and Assassin's Creed|last=Nicholson|first=Matt|publisher=IGN|date=2013-06-21|accessdate=2013-06-21}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。2013年6月，[[法蘭克·馬歇爾|法蘭克·馬歇爾]]進入談判，與[[麥可·法斯賓達|法斯賓達]]、[[康納爾·麥考恩|康納爾·麥考恩]]一同擔任監製<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/frank-marshall-produce-assassins-creed-566356|title=Frank Marshall to Produce 'Assassin's Creed' (Exclusive)|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-06-11|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020041221/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/frank-marshall-produce-assassins-creed-566356|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月，[[史考特·法蘭克|史考特·法蘭克]]透露他已重寫劇本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/08/16/scott-frank-rewriting-assassins-creed-movie|title=Scott Frank Rewriting Assassin's Creed Movie|last=Vejvoda|first=Jim|publisher=IGN|date=2013-08-16|accessdate=2013-08-16|archive-date=2013-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819033239/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/08/16/scott-frank-rewriting-assassins-creed-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月，上映日延至2015年8月17日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/11/12/fantastic-four-reboot-the-secret-service-release-date-changes|title=Fantastic Four Reboot, The Secret Service Release Date Changes|last=Collura|first=Scott|publisher=IGN|date=2013-11-12|accessdate=2013-11-12|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603153840/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/11/12/fantastic-four-reboot-the-secret-service-release-date-changes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年1月，執行製片人[[芬妮·帕尤|芬妮·帕尤]]的個人[[LinkedIn|LinkedIn]]指出，電影將在2014年8月開拍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/25/assassins-creed-movie-to-begin-shooting-in-august-exec-says|title=Assassin's Creed Movie To Begin Shooting In August, Exec Says|last=Mahardy|first=Mike|publisher=IGN|date=2014-01-25|accessdate=2014-01-25|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930185255/https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/01/25/assassins-creed-movie-to-begin-shooting-in-august-exec-says|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年4月，[[比爾·克爾吉|比爾·克爾吉]]和[[亞當·庫珀_(編劇)|亞當·庫珀]]被聘來重寫劇本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/exodus-scribes-adam-cooper-bill-collage-take-assassins-creed/|title=‘Exodus’ Scribes Adam Cooper & Bill Collage Take ‘Assassin’s Creed’|last=Fleming Jr.|first=Mike|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-04-07|accessdate=2014-04-07|archive-date=2014-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410081033/http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/exodus-scribes-adam-cooper-bill-collage-take-assassins-creed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至4月底，[[賈斯汀·克佐|賈斯汀·克佐]]正在進行執導本片的談判<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/04/michael-fassbender-poised-to-re-team-with-macbeth-helmer-on-assassins-creed/|title=Michael Fassbender Poised To Re-Team With ‘Macbeth’ Helmer On ‘Assassin’s Creed’|last=Fleming, Jr.|first=Mike|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-04-29|accessdate=2014-04-29|archive-date=2014-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429230304/http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/michael-fassbender-poised-to-re-team-with-macbeth-helmer-on-assassins-creed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年9月，電影被延遲至2016年的一個未知日期<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/x-men-spin-deadpool-gets-734172|title='X-Men' Spin-Off 'Deadpool' Gets Winter 2016 Release Date|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-09-18|accessdate=2014-09-18}}</ref>，直到2015年1月才確定為2016年12月21日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-01-06-assassins-creed-film-now-due-christmas-2016?utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=socialoomph|title=Assassin's Creed film now due Christmas 2016|author=Tom Phillips|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2015-01-06|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019185021/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-01-06-assassins-creed-film-now-due-christmas-2016?utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=socialoomph|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年2月，該片已進入前期製作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/assassin-s-creed-movie-officially-enters-productio/1100-6425266/|title=Assassin's Creed Movie Officially Enters Production|publisher=Gamespot|last=Makuck|first=Eddie|date=2015-02-12|accessdate=2015-06-29|archive-date=2015-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150630200416/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/assassin-s-creed-movie-officially-enters-productio/1100-6425266/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月，法斯賓達宣布，拍攝將於9月進行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uproxx.com/gammasquad/2015/05/the-michael-fassbender-led-assassins-creed-will-film-this-september/|title=The Michael Fassbender-Led ‘Assassin’s Creed’ Will Film This September|publisher=Uproxx|last=Husband|first=Andrew|date=2015-05-01|accessdate=2015-06-29|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224225301/http://uproxx.com/gammasquad/2015/05/the-michael-fassbender-led-assassins-creed-will-film-this-september/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月22日，馬歇爾對Movie News Guide指出，電影有些地方會和遊戲有所不同，但大致上兩者相距不遠<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.movienewsguide.com/assassins-creed-movie-will-be-different-from-the-game-but-the-same-teases-producer-frank-marshall/70141|title=‘Assassin’s Creed’ Movie Will Be ‘Different from the Game but the Same,’ Teases Producer Frank Marshall|publisher=Movie News Guide|last=Santos|first=Marie delos|date=2015-06-22|access-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626220256/http://www.movienewsguide.com/assassins-creed-movie-will-be-different-from-the-game-but-the-same-teases-producer-frank-marshall/70141|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
2012年7月，[[麥可·法斯賓達|麥可·法斯賓達]]宣布將在片中參演，並透過常與監製[[康納爾·麥考恩|康納爾·麥考恩]]的DMC電影公司來製作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1689211/michael-fassbender-assassins-creed/|title=Michael Fassbender To Star In ‘Assassin’s Creed’|last=Wigler|first=Josh|publisher=MTV|date=2012-07-09|accessdate=2014-08-10|archive-date=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105051343/http://www.mtv.com/news/1689211/michael-fassbender-assassins-creed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。育碧電影首席執行長[[尚-朱利安·巴羅|尚-朱利安·巴羅]]內特表示，[[麥可·法斯賓達|法斯賓達]]是片商擔任主演的首選。2014年6月，[[奧莉薇亞·孟恩|奧莉薇亞·孟恩]]表示有興趣參演<ref>{{cite av media|url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2014/06/26/olivia-munn-wants-to-be-in-the-assassins-creed-movie|title=Olivia Munn Wants to be in Assassin's Creed Movie|publisher=IGN|date=2014-06-26|accessdate=2014-06-26|archive-date=2019-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191105201919/https://www.ign.com/videos/2014/06/26/olivia-munn-wants-to-be-in-the-assassins-creed-movie}}</ref>。2015年2月，[[瑪莉詠·柯蒂亞|瑪莉詠·柯蒂亞]]加入了劇組<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/marion-cotillard-assassins-creed-michael-fassbender-ubisoft-macbeth-12013730277/|title=Marion Cotillard To Star With Michael Fassbender In 'Assassin's Creed' For New Regency & Ubisoft|publisher=Deadline|last=Fleming, Jr|first=Mike|date=2015-02-13}}</ref>。據報導，[[艾莉西亞·薇坎德|艾莉西亞·薇坎德]]正於5月談判出演，但後來她仍沒有加入本片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/05/alicia-vikander-tom-hanks-michael-fassbender-matt-damon-assassins-creed-jason-bourne-the-circle-1201432103/|title=Hot Cannes 'Circle' Package Imperiled As Alicia Vikander In Talks To Star In 'Assassin's Creed', New 'Bourne' Film|publisher=Deadline|last1=Fleming, Jr|first1=Mike|last2=Jaafar|first2=Ali|date=2015-05-22|accessdate=2015-05-22|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926002500/https://deadline.com/2015/05/alicia-vikander-tom-hanks-michael-fassbender-matt-damon-assassins-creed-jason-bourne-the-circle-1201432103/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/alicia-vikander-jason-bourne-sequel-opposite-matt-damon-paul-greengrass-1201452209/|title=Alicia Vikander Confirmed For Bourne Sequel Opposite Matt Damon|publisher=Deadline|last=Fleming, Jr|first=Mike|date=2015-06-23|accessdate=2015-06-29|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203212503/http://deadline.com/2015/06/alicia-vikander-jason-bourne-sequel-opposite-matt-damon-paul-greengrass-1201452209/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔天，據透露，[[阿麗安·拉蓓|阿麗安·拉蓓]]加入飾演艾莉西亞·薇坎德原本在談判的角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/ariane-labed-assassins-creed-michael-fassbender-marion-cotillard-1201453736/|title=Ariane Labed Joins Cast of ‘Assassin’s Creed’ Opposite Michael Fassbender|publisher=Deadline|date=2015-06-24|accessdate=2015-06-25|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626122830/http://deadline.com/2015/06/ariane-labed-assassins-creed-michael-fassbender-marion-cotillard-1201453736/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
正式拍攝於2015年8月31日在[[馬爾他|馬爾他]]、[[倫敦|倫敦]]和[[西班牙|西班牙]]進行<ref>{{cite news|title=Big screen adaptation of Assassin's Creed starts shooting in Malta|url=http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20150903/local/big-screen-adaptation-of-assassins-creed-starts-shooting-in-malta.583021|accessdate=2015-09-04|work=timesofmalta.com|date=2015-09-03|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905164204/http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20150903/local/big-screen-adaptation-of-assassins-creed-starts-shooting-in-malta.583021|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影直至2016年1月15日宣布[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://comicbook.com/2016/01/15/assassins-creed-movie-starring-michael-fassbender-wraps-filming/|title=Assassin's Creed Movie Starring Michael Fassbender Wraps Filming|publisher=Comic Book|last=Jayson|first=Jay|date=2016-01-15|accessdate=2016-01-16|archive-date=2017-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170312054617/http://comicbook.com/2016/01/15/assassins-creed-movie-starring-michael-fassbender-wraps-filming/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
2013年5月，《刺客教條》最初定於2016年5月22日在美國上映。後來經過多次更改才決定定於2016年12月21日上映。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於215條評論，新鮮度18%，平均評分3.97／10；觀眾新鮮度為43%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/assassins_creed |title=Assassin's Creed (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2017-01-12 |archive-date=2018-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617115718/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/assassins_creed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]獲得36分，評價以負面居多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/assassins-creed |title=Assassin's Creed reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222040940/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/assassins-creed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-10-01 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。觀眾和粉絲的評價比影評人好上許多。

=== 票房 ===
《刺客教條》北美於全美2902間電影院上映，票房原先預估前六天可達2500萬至3500萬美元。<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |title=Will ‘Rogue One’ Vanquish The Christmas B.O. Competition? |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216145243/http://deadline.com/2016/12/rogue-one-star-wars-passengers-jennifer-lawrence-sing-collateral-beauty-will-smith-christmas-box-office-1201869720/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，電影在12月20日口碑場的票房僅收入140萬美元，使當週六天預測下修至2200萬美元<ref name="Thursday">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-sing-beats-assassins-creed-passengers-tuesday-previews-958235 |title='Sing's' Box-Office Debut Tops 'Assassin's Creed,' 'Passengers' in Tuesday Night Previews |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2016-12-22 |archive-date=2016-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222041214/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-sing-beats-assassins-creed-passengers-tuesday-previews-958235 |dead-url=no }}</ref>美國首映週末六天累計票房僅2250萬美元，位居當週第五，口碑不佳<ref name="opening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/why-him-975k-thursday-previews-box-office-1201875344/|title=With ‘Fences,’ ‘La La Land’ Enter Top 10 As ‘Rogue One’ & ‘Sing’ Rule Holiday – Monday AM Update|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2016-12-26|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/why-him-975k-thursday-previews-box-office-1201875344/&date=2018-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 後續 ==
2016年3月，負責該片合資的[[威望國際|威望國際]]首席執行長楊麗貞表示，如果電影表現理想，New Regency就推出續集的打算<ref>{{cite web | url=http://variety.com/2016/film/asia/assassins-creed-splinter-cell-sequels-1201735951/ | title=‘Assassin’s Creed,’ ‘Splinter Cell’ Being Eyed for Sequels | work=Variety | date=2016-03-22 | accessdate=2016-03-22 | last=Frater | first=Patrick | archive-date=2020-10-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031181334/https://variety.com/2016/film/asia/assassins-creed-splinter-cell-sequels-1201735951/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而隨著電影商業表現不佳，以及受到[[迪士尼收購21世紀福斯|迪士尼收購21世紀福斯]]等影響，所以續集計劃已經被取消。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://techraptor.net/content/disney-cancels-assassins-creed-film-sequel-mega-man-and-the-sims-movies|title=Disney Cancels Assassin's Creed Film Sequel, Mega Man and The Sims Movies|date=2019-08-11|website=Gaming News, Reviews, and Articles - TechRaptor.net|language=en-US|access-date=2019-08-20|archive-date=2019-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820060618/https://techraptor.net/content/disney-cancels-assassins-creed-film-sequel-mega-man-and-the-sims-movies}}</ref>

